HEADWORD: Testator
<hw>Tes*ta"tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.: cf. F.
<ets>testateur</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A man who makes and
